title: Bridgestone to Buy Auto Parts Retailer Pep Boys for $835M
text:
Published By: Fox Business - Today 
Japanese tire maker Bridgestone said it would buy U.S. auto parts retailer Pep Boys - Manny, Moe & Jack for $835 million in cash....
